{"tid":1446810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇科大人可以發個聯署隊PPRB","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:25:16.000Z","uid":266060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7dbf5e074f90e61259f878ec4a87f734cb2af6","tid":1446810,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:19:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xKtI1Tv0SSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxKtI1Tv0SSA&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ57PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=73a3db24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xKtI1Tv0SSA</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警次次都話「問PPRB」<br />\n但大家都見到，PPRB乜都答「無資料」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然PPRB阿頭謝振中總警司係科大人<br />\n有冇手足都係科大人（甚至知佢咩學系）<br />\n發個聯署叫佢辭職明志<br />\n「既然行動組做乜野都入PPRB數，謝振中唔辭職仲係人？」<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"f545c54a37dbe45feaf2c2321c788af934bf7206","tid":1446810,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4539064ed1c4b7e3f97c6fab61667c0b1772f9d","tid":1446810,"uid":303872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"1baf9802ea534eef2060665b17e39291d433171d","tid":1446810,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should o